&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;You&#39;ll run our content engine and communications: the company&#39;s narrative, blog, social channels, email programs, public relations (with support from our PR agency), and the integrated campaigns that tie it all together. You&#39;ll work in close partnership with our team&#39;s Head of Marketing, Brand Lead, and AI Developer Advocate to put Imbue in front of the people who matter most: builders and the AI community.&lt;/p&gt;
