&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;This role is a particularly good fit for anyone who either has previously been, or would like to be, a founder of a software product company. We are looking primarily for good product intuition and judgment — someone who understands what actually matters and then makes that happen.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
